          "<h2>About Us</h2>\r\nMylekha is a suite of POS (point-of-sale) mobile applications. Our tools help merchants around the world to manage their sales, inventories, employees, and customers.\r\n\r\nThe name stands for the Your Assistant. It reflects our conviction that customer assistant is an essential factor for businesses to be successful.\r\n\r\nOur customers love Mylekha mobile apps for its straightforward to learn and simple to use interface. We believe that by empowering small businesses, which is the backbone of every country’s economy, we contribute to the welfare of humanity.\r\n<h2>Who we are?</h2>\r\nOur team has a foundation of many years of experience in the field of point of sale software development and integrations with payment gateways.\r\n<h2>Feature</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>Install MYLEKHA software on your smartphone or tablet, start your sales, sign up customers.</li>\r\n \t<li>Manage one or multiple stores from the same account. Your analytics are in the cloud, always with you.</li>\r\n \t<li>Increase customer retention, run your own loyalty program, boost your sales.</li>\r\n</ul>",
